ZH: 我昨晚梦见我在海边散步。
EN: I dreamt last night that I was walking by the sea.

ZH: 他常常梦见自己飞翔在天空中。
EN: He often dreams of flying in the sky.

ZH: 我梦见我在一个未知的城市里迷路了。
EN: I dreamt that I got lost in an unknown city.

ZH: 她梦见她的家人都变成了动物。
EN: She dreamt that her family turned into animals.

ZH: 我曾经梦见过世界末日的场景。
EN: I have dreamt of scenes from the end of the world.

ZH: 梦见有人在敲我家窗户时，我吓了一跳。
EN: When I dreamt of someone knocking on my window, I got a fright.

ZH: 我梦见我在一片美丽的花海中漫步。
EN: I dreamt that I was strolling through a beautiful sea of flowers.

ZH: 她梦见她在一个神秘的城堡里探险。
EN: She dreamt of adventuring in a mysterious castle.

ZH: 他竟然梦见他自己变成了超级英雄。
EN: He dreamt that he turned into a superhero.

ZH: 我最近梦见我和我的朋友在一起旅行。
EN: I recently dreamt of traveling with my friends.

ZH: 梦见一个黑暗的森林让我觉得有些毛骨悚然。
EN: Dreaming of a dark forest gave me the creeps.

ZH: 我常常梦见我和我的爷爷在一起。
EN: I often dream of being with my grandfather.

ZH: 梦见自己有鸟儿的翅膀是我最美好的梦想之一。
EN: Dreaming of having wings like a bird is one of my greatest dreams.

