EN: I dreamt of performing together with my idol on stage.

ZH: 他梦见自己是一个古代王子。
EN: He dreamt that he was an ancient prince.

ZH: 梦见自己在大雨中被困让我惊醒了。
EN: Dreaming of being trapped in a heavy rainstorm woke me up.

ZH: 我梦见我在大海中游泳，感觉非常自由。
EN: I dreamt of swimming in the ocean, feeling incredibly free.
